About Chelsea
Chelsea Football Club is a professional football club based in Fulham, London, England, that competes in the Premier League, the top tier of English football. The club was founded in 1905 and is one of the most successful clubs in the history of English football, having won the FA Cup 7 times, the League Cup 5 times, and the UEFA Champions League 1 time. Wikipedia
Palu (Indonesian pronunciation: [pəˈluː]) is the capital city of Central Sulawesi province, Indonesia. It is located on the southeastern coast of the island of Sulawesi. The city has a population of approximately 1.2 million people, making it the third largest city in Sulawesi after Makassar and Manado. Palu is the second largest city in the province of Central Sulawesi, after Makassar. It is also the third largest city in Sulawesi after Makassar and Manado.
The city was founded in the 16th century by the Sultan of Ternate,

Catalan: <s>Donggala és una regentat que s'extenda a més de 300 km (180 milles) de litoral a la costa nord-oriental de la isla de Sulawesi.</s>
Donggala is a regency (kabupaten) of South Sulawesi Province, Indonesia. It is located on the north coast of the island of Sulawesi. The capital of the regency is the town of Donggala. The regency covers an area of 3,000 square kilometres (1,200 sq mi) and has a population of about 300,000 people. The regency is bordered by the regencies of Central Sulawesi to the north, Southeast Sulawesi to the east, Southeast Sulawesi to the south, Southeast Sulawesi to the south, Southeast Sulawesi to the south, Southeast Sulawesi to the south, Southeast Sulawesi to the south, Southeast Sulawesi to the south, Southeast Sulawesi to the south, Southeast Sulawesi to the south, Southeast Sulawesi to the south, Southeast Sulawesi to the south, Southeast Sulawesi to the
